ace":"/rest/api/space/BAN","childTypes":"","schedulePublishInfo":"","operations":"","schedulePublishDate":"","children":"/rest/api/content/2757296194/child","ancestors":"","draftVersion":""},"_links":{"self":"https://qubika.atlassian.net/wiki/rest/api/content/2757296194","tinyui":"/x/QgBZp","editui":"/pages/resumedraft.action?draftId=2757296194","webui":"/spaces/BAN/pages/2757296194/Archived+Initiatives","edituiv2":"/spaces/BAN/pages/edit-v2/2757296194"}},{"id":"2818113569","type":"page","ari":"ari:cloud:confluence:4e3a1a04-13f1-4674-95f6-44812aec1da3:page/2818113569","base64EncodedAri":"YXJpOmNsb3VkOmNvbmZsdWVuY2U6NGUzYTFhMDQtMTNmMS00Njc0LTk1ZjYtNDQ4MTJhZWMxZGEzOmNvbnRlbnQvMjgxODExMzU2OQ==","status":"current","title":"Pix","macroRenderedOutput":{},"extensions":{"position":172687773},"_expandable":{"container":"/rest/api/space/BAN","metadata":"","restrictions":"/rest/api/content/2818113569/restriction/byOperation","history":"/rest/api/content/2818113569/history","body":"","version":"","descendants":"/rest/api/content/2818113569/descendant","space":"/rest/api/space/BAN","childTypes":"","schedulePublishInfo":"","operations":"","schedulePublishDate":"","children":"/rest/api/content/2818113569/child","ancestors":"","draftVersion":""},"_links":{"self":"https://qubika.atlassian.net/wiki/rest/api/content/2818113569","tinyui":"/x/IQD5pw","editui":"/pages/resumedraft.action?draftId=2818113569","webui":"/spaces/BAN/pages/2818113569/Pix","edituiv2":"/spaces/BAN/pages/edit-v2/2818113569"}}],"macroRenderedOutput":{},"body":{"storage":{"value":"<ac:structured-macro ac:name=\"info\" ac:schema-version=\"1\" ac:macro-id=\"85dc5840-7db9-4c8a-802c-75cb7d503897\"><ac:rich-text-body><a href=\"https://bancard.atlassian.net/wiki/spaces/PRYPIX/pages/266993665/Qr+PIX+en+POS+v1.0\" data-card-appearance=\"block\">https://bancard.atlassian.net/wiki/spaces/PRYPIX/pages/266993665/Qr+PIX+en+POS+v1.0</a><p /><p>Responsables: <ac:link><ri:user ri:account-id=\"632e0ea3409249995ee8d951\" /></ac:link> / <ac:link><ri:user ri:account-id=\"637240be489de2f7f4614e6b\" /></ac:link> </p><p>Fecha inicio: <time datetime=\"2024-05-08\" /> </p><p>Fecha entrega: <time datetime=\"2024-05-22\" /> </p><p>Se tiene en cuenta para la estimaci&oacute;n el tiempo de desarrollo, y luego se agregan horas de Management y horas que puedan surgir post salida a Staging. <br />Estas horas post salida a Staging son contempladas para un caso donde no hayan complicaciones de factores externos que bloqueen el desarrollo, ni problemas con proveedores o tareas significativas que puedan surgir. </p><p>En el caso de terminar todo antes, esas horas tambi&eacute;n pueden verse reducidas.</p></ac:rich-text-body></ac:structured-macro><table data-table-width=\"760\" data-layout=\"default\" ac:local-id=\"739bea31-0867-4862-8006-508a1ae1287f\"><colgroup><col style=\"width: 366.0px;\" /><col style=\"width: 124.0px;\" /><col style=\"width: 130.0px;\" /><col style=\"width: 140.0px;\" /></colgroup><tbody><tr><th><p><strong>Tarea</strong></p></th><th><p><strong>Estimaci&oacute;n (hs)</strong></p></th><th><p /></th><th><p><strong>Responsable</strong></p></th></tr><tr><td><p>Nuevo endpoint para generacion de QRs para POS.</p></td><td><p>32</p></td><td><p>external-commerce</p></td><td><p><ac:link><ri:user ri:account-id=\"632e0ea3409249995ee8d951\" /></ac:link> </p></td></tr><tr><td><p>Modificar endpoint de generaci&oacute;n de QRs para recibir el origen, tipo de POS y revisar si es necesario devolver alg&uacute;n par&aacute;metro extra en la respuesta. Guardar tipo de POS para la notificaci&oacute;n (crear columna nueva en el hook).</p></td><td><p>8</p></td><td><p>pix-service</p></td><td><p><ac:link><ri:user ri:account-id=\"632e0ea3409249995ee8d951\" /></ac:link> </p></td></tr><tr><td data-highlight-colour=\"#ffffff\"><p>Guardar RMerchantCode en la respuesta de la notificaci&oacute;n del pago al RPG porque luego se va a enviar en el callback al POS</p></td><td data-highlight-colour=\"#ffffff\"><p>8</p></td><td data-highlight-colour=\"#ffffff\"><p>pix-service</p></td><td data-highlight-colour=\"#ffffff\"><p><ac:link><ri:user ri:account-id=\"637240be489de2f7f4614e6b\" /></ac:link> </p></td></tr><tr><td><p>Implementar l&oacute;gica para notificar al portal cuando el QR se crea desde el portal y al POS cuando se crea desde el POS.</p></td><td><p>32</p></td><td><p>pix-service</p></td><td><p><ac:link><ri:user ri:account-id=\"637240be489de2f7f4614e6b\" /></ac:link> </p></td></tr><tr><td><p>Modificar roles de los POS y agregar el nuevo rol en el authorizer con permiso para todas las operaciones de selling y pix.</p></td><td><p>16</p></td><td><p>external-commerce</p></td><td><p><ac:link><ri:user ri:account-id=\"637240be489de2f7f4614e6b\" /></ac:link> </p></td></tr><tr><td><p>Agregar columna de status interno de bancard para saber si se pudo hacer la notificaci&oacute;n al POS y hacer los cambios para actualizar esa columna.</p></td><td><p>8</p></td><td><p>pix-service</p></td><td><p><ac:link><ri:user ri:account-id=\"637240be489de2f7f4614e6b\" /></ac:link> </p></td></tr><tr><td><p>Tenemos que enviar currency a PIX. Para enviar el monto en guaranies.</p><p>Desde POS, todos los pagos van a ser en GS.</p></td><td><p>24</p></td><td><p>pix-service</p></td><td><p><ac:link><ri:user ri:account-id=\"632e0ea3409249995ee8d951\" /></ac:link> </p></td></tr><tr><td><p>Agregar una column en el dataset de payments para filtrar ventas de acuerdo a si es POS o no</p></td><td><p>4</p></td><td><p>pix-service</p></td><td><p><ac:link><ri:user ri:account-id=\"632e0ea3409249995ee8d951\" /></ac:link> </p></td></tr><tr><td><p>No mostrar en el reporte de ventas de pix-portal aquellas ventas que son del POS. <br />Modificar el q que env&iacute;a pix-portal para filtrar por ventas del POS</p></td><td><p>16</p></td><td><p>pix-portal</p></td><td><p><ac:link><ri:user ri:account-id=\"637240be489de2f7f4614e6b\" /></ac:link> </p></td></tr><tr><td data-highlight-colour=\"#eae6ff\"><p>Total Desarrollo</p></td><td data-highlight-colour=\"#eae6ff\"><p>148</p></td><td data-highlight-colour=\"#eae6ff\"><p /></td><td data-highlight-colour=\"#eae6ff\"><p /></td></tr><tr><td data-highlight-colour=\"#eae6ff\"><p>Total trabajo post deploy a Staging</p><p><em>Incluye tareas de soporte, bug fixing, mejoras, pruebas con rendimento, puesta y deploy a staging + producci&oacute;n, entre otras.</em></p></td><td data-highlight-colour=\"#eae6ff\"><p>40</p></td><td data-highlight-colour=\"#eae6ff\"><p /></td><td data-highlight-colour=\"#eae6ff\"><p /></td></tr><tr><td data-highlight-colour=\"#eae6ff\"><p>Management (15% para facturaci&oacute;n. No afecta la fecha de entrega)</p></td><td data-highlight-colour=\"#eae6ff\"><p>28</p></td><td data-highlight-colour=\"#eae6ff\"><p /></td><td data-highlight-colour=\"#eae6ff\"><p /></td></tr><tr><td data-highlight-colour=\"#f4f5f7\"><p><strong>Total horas de desarrollo Pix en POS</strong></p></td><td data-highlight-colour=\"#f4f5f7\"><p><strong>216</strong></p></td><td data-highlight-colour=\"#f4f5f7\"><p /></td><td data-highlight-colour=\"#f4f5f7\"><p /></td></tr></tbody></table>","representation":"storage","embeddedContent":[],"_expandable":{"content":"/rest/api/content/3051716655"}},"_expandable":{"editor":"","atlas_doc_format":"","view":"","export_view":"","styled_view":"","dynamic":"","editor2":"","anonymous_export_view":""}},"extensions":{"position":1676},"_expandable":{"childTypes":"","container":"/rest/api/space/BAN","schedulePublishInfo":"","metadata":"","operations":"","schedulePublishDate":"","children":"/rest/api/content/3051716655/child","restrictions":"/rest/api/content/3051716655/restriction/byOperation","history":"/rest/api/content/3051716655/history","draftVersion":"","descendants":"/rest/api/content/3051716655/descendant","space":"/rest/api/space/BAN"},"_links":{"editui":"/pages/resumedraft.action?draftId=3051716655","webui":"/spaces/BAN/pages/3051716655/PIX+en+POS+-+Tasking+y+Estimaci+n","edituiv2":"/spaces/BAN/pages/edit-v2/3051716655","context":"/wiki","self":"https://qubika.atlassian.net/wiki/rest/api/content/3051716655","tinyui":"/x/L4DltQ","collection":"/rest/api/content","base":"https://qubika.atlassian.net/wiki"}}